# 🎓 Certifications — Frank Oduro
 
> 30 free, self-paced certifications mapped directly to 7 portfolio projects and 28 KSTU modules.
> Built before Day 1 of lectures. Every certificate earned is linked here.
 
**[▶ View Live Portfolio →](https://ofrank-design.github.io)**
 
---
 
## Structure
 
Certifications are organised in three tiers:
 
| Tier | Count | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| 🥇 **Core 7** | 7 certs | One certificate per portfolio project — direct 1:1 mapping |
| ➕ **Additional 3** | 3 certs | Strong supporting credentials that reinforce multiple projects |
| 🔵 **Optional 5** | 5 certs | Good-to-have skills — completed as each year/module arrives |
| 📚 **Remaining 15** | 15 certs | Full coverage across ERP, logistics, contracts, business, analytics |
 
